<title>USA: US Stockpile sells remaining indium to HOC Metals.</title>
<headline>US Stockpile sells remaining indium to HOC Metals.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-03-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>U.S. Defense National Stockpile Center said it sold 35,956 troy ounces of indium for a total $365,317 to HOC Metals Inc.</p>
<p>The deal was equivalent to a unit price of $10.16 per ounce.</p>
<p>The sale exhausted the amount of indium authorised for sale in the current fiscal year.</p>
<p>((New York Commodity Desk 212-859-1646))</p>
